Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:12.21,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, my name is Ooishi Minori.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:15.44,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,{\i1}The landlord of this place, Mon Paradis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.51,0:00:22.75,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,{\i1}My duty is to always see my residents off cheerfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.42,0:00:26.65,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this morning, I don't feel so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:32.46,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Who would litter like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:35.46,petto,woman,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Mr. Landlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:39.27,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Kusunoki-san from apartment 407! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:40.34,petto,woman,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.24,0:00:44.44,petto,woman,0,0,0,,Umm… it may just be a mistake on my part,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.51,0:00:48.21,petto,woman,0,0,0,,but I heard there's someone on our floor who has a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:50.18,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,What! A pet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.99,0:01:04.13,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh, no. I don't think I can stop now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.57,0:01:11.87,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.97,0:01:12.07,petto overlap,Sumire,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:15.80,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't whine! I told you, no kissing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:19.27,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,But you were sleeping so peacefully and looked so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.04,0:01:20.81,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.21,0:01:23.00,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I won't do it again. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.00,0:01:24.25,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You're the real thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.11,0:01:29.08,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You really, really are Momo, aren't you? You came back?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:31.25,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Sumire-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.46,0:01:37.49,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thank goodness! I was so worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.73,0:01:41.83,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.10,0:01:45.37,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:48.27,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}a boy as a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.11,0:01:54.08,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I found him wounded and soaked by the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.48,0:01:56.68,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}His name is Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.61,0:01:59.91,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Momo doesn't complain about the fact that he is shorter than me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.91,0:02:03.45,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}has no educational background, or has less income than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:07.19,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is because he is simply my pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:09.69,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:14.26,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want you to misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:16.93,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I may be taking care of him, but that's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:19.83,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meaning there is nothing between us in terms of sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:22.80,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Because even if a pet is male, it's not a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:25.61,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Recently, I also got a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:28.68,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hasumi-senpai, whom I've always admired.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:34.12,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought he was out of my league, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:40.36,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,You said you weren't planning on seeing anyone for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:43.73,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Is it all right if I go meet your pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:46.80,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I am constantly busy with my pet,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:50.03,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}and trying to become a better woman for my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:51.77,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyday is like a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:56.24,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Your meals really are the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:03:00.41,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hey, if you're going to leave a letter behind, put it someplace where I can find it easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:01.58,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:06.51,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Do you have a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:08.72,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Mmm… I've not been feeling very well lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:11.45,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,That's because you don't sleep under the blankets properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.22,0:03:14.72,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,The house dust at the hotel I was staying in was awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:15.72,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:17.73,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was in Takazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:20.16,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,For a dance seminar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:24.67,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:28.70,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,After you finish that, why don't you take some medicine and go to sleep again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:30.71,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,If you don't get more rest, you'll develop asthma again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:35.81,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:37.31,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:39.45,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,are you happy when I'm around?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:40.05,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:43.22,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,You look like you're having fun today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:44.75,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Not particularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:47.56,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Because you ate so happily, the mood just got carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:54.73,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What are you doing? You're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:58.03,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I'm just happy that you're so worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:02.94,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,From now on, I'll wait patiently for you to come home every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:08.04,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Next time you're gone, I'll put a dog tag on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:11.01,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.99,0:04:24.33,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}A lot has happened, but I have no complaints. I'm happy with my current life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:30.50,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope that these bright days will continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:38.34,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,It's decided. I'm going on that exchange programme to Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:40.48,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I'm going to leave in June.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:43.04,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Give sensei my regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:45.45,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Takeshi-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:49.15,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,That's all. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:05:00.52,title,text,0,0,0,,{\pos(434,140)\blur0.7}You are my pet
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:05:00.52,episode,text,0,0,0,,{\pos(434,377)\blur0.6}4. Love infection
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:07.15,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Shiba dog, Husky, Maltese, Beagle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:11.14,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Corgi, German Shepherd, Yorkshire Terrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:13.98,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Poodle and Border Collie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:17.11,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,French Bul and Cocker Spaniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:20.32,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,And don't forget the longhaired Chihuahua, Pitt-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:25.12,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,It almost sounds like we're naming flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:27.99,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,You're right that dogs have soft names.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:30.56,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Their names ofter begin with H and R sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:34.66,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Soft things have the power to heal one's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:37.10,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Soft things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:38.77,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.43,0:05:44.07,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Soft things, little things, warm things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:50.85,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,The human brain is programmed to feel healed by such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:54.95,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Soft, little and warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:57.00,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:58.55,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:05.09,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.53,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,That movie was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:13.00,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was moved to tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:18.11,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I have a soft spot for movies like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:21.18,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,If I had been watching it alone at home, I would have been sobbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.18,0:06:22.18,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:25.35,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Especially movies about animals and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:29.08,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh! I remember you bawling while you were reporting about a hippopotamus giving birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:31.62,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Please don't bring that up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:41.02,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:47.04,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thanks goodness! We still have time. It was at three o'clock, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:50.24,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, the speech by the Austrian president.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:56.44,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,With our current work shifts, I always have night duty when you get days off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.28,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,"Our"…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:09.06,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Let's go. We have to make the best out of the next hour and a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:21.07,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Wow, they look like models! Such a picture perfect couple, don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:23.07,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Kokeshi doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:23.94,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:27.74,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Stiff. Iwaya-san is too stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:29.11,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:37.32,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,She and I…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:46.26,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I going to do? This is a dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:50.40,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}The area beneath my left ear is itching.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:58.07,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if I scratch it with my right hand, my posture will look very awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:01.41,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Plus, I'm carrying a purse. Worse still, it's colorful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:07.25,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}But… There's no way I can let go of this hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.85,0:08:10.05,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll ignore it. Just don't think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:13.36,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, Iwaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:16.93,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Why don't we try that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:22.60,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What? Sticker photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:25.97,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Actually, I don't even have a single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.71,0:08:35.18,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Personally, I don't really like taking photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:43.82,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,There! I've inserted money inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:51.29,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I wonder what they mean by preferred pose?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:53.70,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Do you think there might actually be someone inside these machines?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:56.35,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:56.97,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:09:00.80,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wha… What can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:02.64,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Shall we decide on pink?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:08.71,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, it turned pink! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:12.85,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, our faces are somehow on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:15.22,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, there's the camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:18.92,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wa… Wait!! That… just now…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:30.40,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Wow! The colors are pretty vivid in these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.50,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm not very good with photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:34.80,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:39.01,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,That's the worst. I want to throw it away. I would like to erase it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:42.78,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,That bad? It reminds me of the time back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.37,0:09:43.88,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.55,0:09:46.18,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,The time when we took a photo together back in Kofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:51.09,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,When you came to see me off to Rio de Janeiro…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:55.09,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I still treasure that picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:00.23,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Treasure…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:05.47,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:06.67,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:11.04,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing. I was very happy to be able to see you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:15.28,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I wonder where I should stick this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:28.06,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,This half is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:29.32,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:35.00,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:39.00,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Are you all right? You're not sick, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:40.84,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It's rather breezy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:43.84,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, no. Not at all. Please excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:47.48,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:05.03,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I should get rid of the smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:10.17,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:15.24,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Maybe I do have a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:18.21,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Are you okay? If you want, I have some nasal decongestant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:22.48,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Thanks, Junpei. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:23.41,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:26.15,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Oh, so we love each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.31,0:11:27.38,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.82,0:11:33.25,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,I just thought about how proud I should be, that a friend of mine could get into the International Contemporary Dance Competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:36.83,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,I'm so proud, yet a little envious too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:41.16,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,You can jump so high and you have sucha a beautiful girl worrying about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:43.03,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,It feels like it's healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:47.10,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Whenever Rumi calls, it's always about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:49.00,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I'm envious of you, too. Of your…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:55.10,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,When you take happiness for granted, you become greedier and greedier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:57.60,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,It's the sad saga of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:12:00.15,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,In that sense, pets are nice and simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.50,0:12:04.50,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,But don't pets sometimes become greedy, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:08.19,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,They do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:12.79,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,But if a pet became too greedy, they would just be abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:19.57,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,And because they understand that fully, they'll listen obediently to what their master says.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:23.84,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,It's going to be okay, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:26.91,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Takeshi. It's going to be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:34.35,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have worn new shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:43.79,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:45.93,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, here. It looked good so I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:03.58,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Can you move towards the edge a little more?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:04.01,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:08.92,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:19.13,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Senpai, our coworkers might see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:20.53,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I don't mind if we're seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:23.06,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,We don't have any policy against office romances.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:38.25,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Are you sure you have the time for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:45.25,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,He fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:58.07,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,There, there…\NWhat am I doing…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:08.88,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,When I'm like this, I feel really calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:33.72,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, that's mine. I'm sorry, I think it's from the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:37.04,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Shiorin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.61,0:14:44.05,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I wonder who it is… Maybe Shiohara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:49.72,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't know. I've never heard anyone call Shiohara-san "Shiorin".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:51.19,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.96,0:14:55.79,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:59.86,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, I was wondering who it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:06.90,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Really? That's awful. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:09.64,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,You shouldn't get involved anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:13.07,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Just leave it alone, and it'll be better for you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:17.05,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Okay, later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:20.65,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,No, now is not a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:22.42,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I have night duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:26.86,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Tomorrow? I really don't know about then…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:30.29,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, I'll hear about it some other time, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:31.50,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:37.43,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, she just kept talking so I couldn't find a good time to cut her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:38.67,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh no, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:39.80,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It was from Fukushima-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:41.80,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?! Fukushima-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.91,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Apparently, she broke up with her boyfriend recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:46.71,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,And he keeps following her around and she's been seeking advice from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:48.41,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:52.08,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,The other day, I was having lunch with her at the company cafeteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.08,0:15:55.62,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,She didn't know how to use the company cell phone, so she asked me for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:59.89,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,And then, apparently she entered her own number into my phone. I'm so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:02.49,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, what a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.43,0:16:07.00,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at that, it's a made-up story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:11.50,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,I think it's safe to say that the enemy has the upper hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.93,0:16:13.20,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,The "enemy"…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:14.14,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,She's an enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:16.54,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,My head hurts. Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.54,0:16:19.54,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I do see! Last time, she tried to break up our date directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:22.98,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Besides, you've been going out with this guy for two weeks already,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:24.45,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,and you haven't let him into your pants yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:26.41,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You shouldn't say such things in front of a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.41,0:16:28.48,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,She doesn't understand, so it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:30.89,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,If you don't act quick, she'll steal him with sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:31.59,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:35.62,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Wait, are you sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:37.76,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't know, I'm getting the chills.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:42.20,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Sumire-chan! I cleaned up, so forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:44.57,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, five more minutes. Clean from corner to corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:50.64,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,He left the toilet seat up, so I'm punishing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.64,0:16:52.74,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,To enforce punishment immediately after a wrongdoing is the fundamentals of discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:58.41,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,But I wonder if Fukushima-san really likes Hasumi-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.05,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,You're too nonchalant, Sumire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.05,0:17:02.25,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,You can't just wait around and expect to still be connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:04.85,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,The relationships between men and women aren't that simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:06.96,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Why don't you invite him for a change?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:12.99,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Like, "Umm… Is it okay if I go over to your place next time?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:14.40,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I can't say such a shallow phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:15.60,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Stop trying to keep that cool façade!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:16.87,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to look cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:19.43,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,That's really not cute, that side of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:22.07,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,You can't even smoke a cigarette in front of senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:24.04,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,What kind of a relationship are you in,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:26.01,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,when you can't even be yourself in front of your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.01,0:17:28.18,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's not that I can't show my true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:30.28,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:30.28,petto overlap,Momo,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Sumire-chan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:32.98,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Should I arrange the pads in order from heavy to light?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:34.78,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Huh? No, don't touch those!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:36.15,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wait, Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.22,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,I guess she shouldn't be herself too much in front of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:45.89,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Looks like it's around 37.2 degrees Celsius.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:50.93,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I thought it was just another one of those headaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:54.04,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I might have passed on my cold to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:56.71,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:00.51,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:04.21,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Are you that happy that I'm sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:05.15,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:10.05,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I'm just drunk with the thought that I've infected you with my virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:11.79,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:14.62,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hurt yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:18.33,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yeah, a blister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:20.70,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,From walking too much in my new shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:23.63,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,The pair you bought for your date!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:31.91,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm not sick anymore, so can I sleep next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:34.08,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Huh? Why? No, you can't! Get out now! Scram!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:35.35,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.54,0:18:38.75,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Take care, master.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:40.15,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:50.63,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Was I that scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:54.60,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Okay! The other papers haven't gotten hold of that news yet, have they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:58.53,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,No matter what, I want to publish it in the morning papers. We'll handle the editing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:00.34,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:18.85,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Come to think of it…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:29.56,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:31.33,announcement,text,0,0,0,,{\an7}Setaya's 15-year old: Goda Takeshi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:42.44,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I feel terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:44.35,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,That's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:46.98,petto overlap,colleague,0,0,0,,It's true! She kept looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.98,0:19:48.02,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:49.40,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,I feel love in the air…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:52.25,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,She doesn't seem to have a care in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:57.33,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,Iwaya, have you gotten that story about the vaccine ready for next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.39,0:19:59.59,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll turn it in before the conference meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:01.50,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,along with the review for Dr. Ogawa's novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:04.13,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,That's done, too? That's fast of Dr. Ogawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.13,0:20:07.00,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll bring it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:08.84,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,So cyborgs get sick, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:09.47,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:13.64,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,Don't give it to me. The masks are sold in the drugstore upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:16.50,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:17.90,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Uriyama-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:18.38,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:20.28,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,I finally found Carlos!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:21.55,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:23.89,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,She's a beauty! I put her on my screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:26.72,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Well, it's just an ordinary cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.32,0:20:31.29,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,That's awful! Hasumi-san told me she was cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:34.13,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,He's nice to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.20,0:20:36.93,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.87,0:20:40.97,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Shoot, I forgot the floppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.64,0:20:42.64,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.64,0:20:44.27,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:47.91,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh, and this is the medicine you have to take with lunch. You left it on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:51.45,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I totally forgot to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:54.92,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Are you okay? You were out of sorts in the morning, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:58.79,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yeah… I think I'll go home early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.85,0:21:00.99,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.06,0:21:04.96,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's a reward. Open it when you get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:09.40,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wait… What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:10.30,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:11.87,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't kiss me in public!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:13.67,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,But I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:19.04,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Iwaya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:21.04,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Ishida-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:26.35,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Oh, err… Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:29.35,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Uh… A young boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:31.25,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No… This is… Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.25,0:21:33.40,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. I'm her younger brother, Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.45,0:21:34.79,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Oh, your younger brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:37.83,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you for always looking out for my older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.93,0:21:40.56,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.56,0:21:43.13,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,He just came back from France, so he's a little touchy-feely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.26,0:21:45.43,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oui, bonjour!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.04,0:21:52.61,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Oh, so that's what it was! I was so surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.77,0:21:54.24,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I was surprised as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:21:57.78,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Our hometown is in Chiba, but my sister wanted me to stop by here. So I was just stopping by.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.85,0:21:58.81,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Right, sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.78,0:22:01.92,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:04.02,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,But you look nothing like Iwaya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.02,0:22:04.59,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.75,0:22:07.09,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:09.29,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Maybe because I look more like my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:11.56,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,That must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.76,0:22:15.20,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Iwaya-san has Hasumi-san from External Affairs, so there should be no such thing as…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:16.30,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.30,0:22:17.53,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be heading back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:19.73,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,You're lucky to have such a wonderful sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.30,0:22:22.60,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Let's take good care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.58,0:22:29.91,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work, Hamada-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.55,0:22:33.38,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Merci beaucoup, monsieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.92,0:22:36.42,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Who looks like my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.62,0:22:39.29,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,That Ishida-kun seems to be interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:40.42,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What? Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.49,0:22:43.32,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,But it's true that I have a sister in Chiba. Actually three.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:46.66,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Three sisters? But my hometown is in Yokohama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.66,0:22:48.50,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:51.27,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,But I'm relieved that we didn't spill the beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.13,0:22:55.47,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't know what I'd do if people found out I had a boy as a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.37,0:22:57.31,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.81,0:23:00.64,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks for this. Good luck at your lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:01.74,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.69,0:23:19.13,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,And… I don't want to be repetitive, but please follow the deadlines.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.13,0:23:20.30,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,All right, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.30,0:23:21.63,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:29.77,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, my throat hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.91,0:23:34.11,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hasumi-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.58,0:23:38.61,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.61,0:23:39.75,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Can I have a moment with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.58,0:23:41.42,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.42,0:23:42.42,petto,colleaguei,0,0,0,,All right, later.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.56,0:23:58.07,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,I heard from Junpei.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.14,0:24:02.84,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,You're living with a career woman right now, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.84,0:24:04.91,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Yeah, but it's more like…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.91,0:24:06.17,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,So you live off her money like a pimp?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.64,0:24:09.08,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I'm her pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.38,0:24:12.05,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,What's that? That's worse, you're not even a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.11,0:24:14.18,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,That may be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.02,0:24:17.55,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,Did you break up with me because you wanted to be with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.55,0:24:18.59,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Huh? What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.59,0:24:19.92,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,You were the one who broke up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.92,0:24:24.49,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,I just thought that if I said I wanted to break up,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.53,0:24:27.10,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,you would say that you don't want to, and like me even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.26,0:24:29.93,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,That's so unreasonable. You're hard to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.90,0:24:35.94,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,Then kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.34,0:24:39.77,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Are you going home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.21,0:24:44.21,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Yeah, things were kind of hectic in the morning, with the news from Palestine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.21,0:24:47.68,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,That must have been difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.32,0:24:55.76,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Kuraki-san told me,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.29,0:24:59.03,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,that you were sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.49,0:25:00.03,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.53,0:25:04.27,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I was worried that it was because I dragged you around the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.57,0:25:06.30,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Not at all. It's really nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.10,0:25:08.50,petto overlap,Hasumi,0,0,0,,No, but that day…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.50,0:25:10.67,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,it seemed like there was something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.94,0:25:12.94,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Really, there wasn't. You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.94,0:25:14.18,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Of course I'd worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.31,0:25:19.35,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It seems like you're constantly worrying about satisfying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.08,0:25:23.42,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,You know, maybe because I was your senior back at Kofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.85,0:25:26.12,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.12,0:25:28.06,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It may not be such a big deal…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.19,0:25:35.23,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,But the fact that I was the only one who didn't know about your sickness…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.46,0:25:38.93,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It made me a little sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.67,0:25:44.15,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,You can be more personal with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.75,0:25:50.85,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.38,0:25:57.55,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,No. If you apologize, it will make me feel worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.70,0:26:04.33,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Hasumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.59,0:26:07.60,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Fukushima-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.27,0:26:12.33,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for calling you so often.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.23,0:26:15.27,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,After calling you yesterday, it got even worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.27,0:26:17.37,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,He kept bothering me and bothering me with phone calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.51,0:26:19.47,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,And I'm scared, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.21,0:26:22.58,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Would it be okay if I stayed at your place tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.84,0:26:23.41,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.75,0:26:27.00,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,When I saw your personal particulars, I noticed you live really close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.00,0:26:29.45,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I live on the 4th block, along Meiji Road.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.82,0:26:30.52,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.52,0:26:31.12,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.15,0:26:33.96,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,And I felt that we had some sort of connection,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.09,0:26:35.85,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,and I actually still feel…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.95,0:26:38.36,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Umm, I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.73,0:26:39.43,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.06,0:26:44.50,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I still have some work left to do. So please, take your time. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.47,0:26:46.50,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Iwaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.10,0:26:51.27,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Iwaya-san is so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.24,0:26:55.21,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I can't be strong like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.52,0:27:39.75,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,I still like you, Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.59,0:27:44.29,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,Do you like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.23,0:27:47.46,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Yeah, I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.86,0:27:53.20,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,People will come by here. Let's go somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.74,0:27:57.77,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Well, I can't take you to a love hotel. I don't have any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.24,0:27:59.37,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,Then I'll pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.74,0:28:02.44,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,And even if we go, I'll leave in half an hour's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.45,0:28:05.85,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,It's around the time that she'll be coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.68,0:28:11.25,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Do you still want to go? Or do you want to continue here?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.62,0:28:15.12,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,You're mean! I hope you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.33,0:28:26.33,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.77,0:28:29.14,petto,Rumi,0,0,0,,Junpei!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.54,0:28:34.91,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Is it Takeshi again?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.35,0:29:22.36,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Takeshi-san is scheduled to leave at the beginning of June.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.92,0:29:25.66,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Yes, I checked with the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.70,0:29:30.03,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,They're a pretty well-known group in Frankfurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.27,0:29:33.44,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Yes, the period is to be about three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.30,0:29:41.78,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,How about it, sensei? Why don't you sit down and talk to Takeshi beforehand?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.45,0:29:45.81,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Oh… Well, I will contact you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.45,0:29:53.46,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Oh, so pets are not allowed here?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.46,0:29:56.96,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Yes. It was on the move-in brochure, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.19,0:29:59.53,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Have you not read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.66,0:30:04.43,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,I did read it. It was the fourth column on the fourth page.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.63,0:30:05.57,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.34,0:30:09.90,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Oh… Iwaya-san, may I have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.90,0:30:11.07,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.57,0:30:13.58,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,That woman is always so unfriendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.38,0:30:16.11,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.05,0:30:20.82,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,I would like to know a little more about that young woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.53,0:30:31.53,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.07,0:30:40.57,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo, you're not home again? You told me you'd be waiting every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.61,0:30:48.94,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.61,0:30:51.58,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.85,0:30:57.82,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh… Sumire-chan, welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.39,0:31:02.02,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I was thinking about something, and I guess I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.66,0:31:03.79,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What a strange child.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.39,0:31:06.19,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.90,0:31:13.54,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I was very happy with my reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.37,0:31:16.17,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's not much.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.30,0:31:18.87,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I just thought it was inconvenient that I couldn't get in touch with you sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.48,0:31:28.00,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm tired. Is retort good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.00,0:31:30.22,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,It's fine, I can make it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.35,0:31:33.79,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I'll just eat the frozen curry we had last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.79,0:31:39.79,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to eat anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.66,0:31:44.07,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't have an appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.14,0:31:48.94,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Did something happen with your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.07,0:31:50.51,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.74,0:31:51.91,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I wonder why…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.11,0:31:55.91,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,For some reason, I can always tell what you're thinking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.91,0:31:56.75,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.01,0:32:00.38,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Because I'm a pet, I think it's an animal's instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.75,0:32:04.22,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Momo…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.52,0:32:07.06,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,My dog, Momo…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.96,0:32:11.49,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Whenever I was down, it would always be by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.66,0:32:15.46,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,There were a lot of things that got me depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.60,0:32:19.20,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,My parents were always fighting with each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.20,0:32:21.47,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,and my grandfather disciplined us strictly.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.24,0:32:24.91,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,My parents were always fighting, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.24,0:32:26.17,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.17,0:32:26.68,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.88,0:32:29.58,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,My mother wanted me to do ballet,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.58,0:32:32.18,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,and my father ridiculed men going into ballet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.18,0:32:33.31,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Always fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.62,0:32:35.75,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.25,0:32:38.72,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,But my older sisters always took good care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.56,0:32:41.79,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.32,0:32:44.63,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,You finally smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.70,0:32:50.73,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I think you should relax more.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.27,0:32:55.70,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,When people like each other, they're supposed to have more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.14,0:32:58.37,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.37,0:32:59.07,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.47,0:33:05.01,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,They're supposed to say "I love you" over and over like idiots,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.41,0:33:07.58,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,kiss each other, and sleep with each other…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.58,0:33:09.35,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I can't be like those idiotic couples!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.35,0:33:10.65,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Idiotic couples are good.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.82,0:33:12.89,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Because if you think too deeply, it'll hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.62,0:33:14.99,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Easier said than done.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.02,0:33:17.33,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,It's easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.77,0:33:27.70,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.35,0:33:40.25,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,See? Like that, it's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.38,0:33:42.72,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Ouch! Why'd you hit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.32,0:33:46.29,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I just felt like it… You just made me mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.22,0:33:49.32,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Hey, your cheeks are red.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.72,0:33:50.16,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.86,0:33:53.76,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's my fever. I have a fever! I'm sick, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.30,0:33:56.00,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Are you going to sleep in those clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.00,0:33:57.20,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm fine, just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.33,0:34:00.20,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,All right, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.44,0:34:06.51,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Gosh…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.48,0:34:10.18,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You're a pet, don't exert weird pheromones…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.80,0:34:33.77,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.44,0:34:35.94,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,This is my phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.01,0:34:40.78,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Make sure you record it in your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.78,0:34:44.41,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.48,0:34:48.32,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Can you wake me up around eleven?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.78,0:34:50.09,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I need to take my medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.45,0:34:52.32,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.53,0:34:58.73,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Tomorrow will be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.47,0:35:04.17,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.13,0:35:07.54,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.71,0:35:11.57,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.55,0:35:27.66,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.72,0:35:33.26,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,No way. I can't say it. I've never said anything like that in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.53,0:35:35.46,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,It sounds like the lyrics to some pop song.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.56,0:35:38.53,petto,girl,0,0,0,,Hey, wasn't today's hamburger rice delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.04,0:35:43.24,petto,girl,0,0,0,,The omelette rice was really good too! Let's go again. Yeah, let's go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.84,0:35:46.21,petto,girl,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, we overheard
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.21,0:35:48.64,petto,girl,0,0,0,,Iwaya-san and Hasumi-san talking on the rooftop the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.88,0:35:53.35,petto,girl,0,0,0,,And on top of that, it was like "Enter Fukushima-chan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.92,0:35:55.82,petto,girl,0,0,0,,And then Iwaya-san just left…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.82,0:35:56.79,petto,girl,0,0,0,,And… and…?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.85,0:35:58.45,petto,girl,0,0,0,,Hasumi-san told Fukushima-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.92,0:36:02.62,petto,girl,0,0,0,,"Sorry, I'm planning on spending my days off with my girlfriend."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.82,0:36:05.59,petto,girl,0,0,0,,How dreamy…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.59,0:36:09.56,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm planning on spending my days off with my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.67,0:36:11.50,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.80,0:36:13.50,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Yes, with Iwaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.57,0:36:19.01,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,And, I have a policy not to let anyone but my girlfriend into my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.35,0:36:25.35,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Well, I'll call you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.45,0:36:31.09,petto,girl,0,0,0,,The way he was firm was attractive, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.86,0:36:39.66,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a happy idiot I am…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.76,0:36:42.90,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.51,0:36:54.84,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hasumi-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.51,0:36:58.55,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Iwaya…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.62,0:37:06.25,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.30,0:37:09.30,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.00,0:37:16.20,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.10,0:37:22.74,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry about the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.84,0:37:25.91,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,And…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.91,0:37:29.64,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,And… senpai, you have tomorrow off, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.01,0:37:31.81,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.98,0:37:34.02,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I can take many days off this month,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.38,0:37:36.89,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,so I was thinking I might take the day off tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.92,0:37:38.99,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,And…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.66,0:37:42.52,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,And… Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.63,0:37:45.96,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Then will you come over?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.96,0:37:46.63,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.23,0:37:48.63,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Tonight, to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.40,0:37:57.10,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.94,0:38:01.78,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.35,0:38:08.62,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Look, I stuck it on right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.92,0:38:10.65,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I hate this ugly-faced picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.65,0:38:12.09,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Huh? You look cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.89,0:38:16.96,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I like how you look. Like you're not putting up any kind of façade.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.80,0:38:22.00,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Is your cold better?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.80,0:38:24.37,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh yes, I'm all better.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.97,0:38:27.27,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Then, I'll be looking forward to tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.70,0:38:28.60,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.02,0:38:40.82,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.82,0:38:42.12,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Thank you, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.04,0:39:05.27,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I want to be more like myself around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.53,0:39:31.33,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Iwaya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.80,0:39:35.40,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh… Doctor, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.44,0:39:37.14,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,I was about to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.11,0:39:40.04,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Overtime by yourself, I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.34,0:39:41.68,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, just a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.08,0:39:44.68,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I left early yesterday because I had a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.68,0:39:46.18,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.22,0:39:51.55,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Well, you are truly very hardworking and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.49,0:39:54.39,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,That's not so…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.09,0:39:58.33,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,I saw you at the park the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.36,0:39:59.83,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Huh? When?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.33,0:40:03.03,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Probably the day you got that blister.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.30,0:40:05.97,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.70,0:40:11.91,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,You and I are alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.17,0:40:15.04,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.75,0:40:18.61,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Well, how do I say…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.65,0:40:28.26,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,I can love what the world is supposed to love, such as pets, mothers and children…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.99,0:40:32.56,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,But I cannot love a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.36,0:40:36.77,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.77,0:40:37.77,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,You are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.17,0:40:43.00,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,You cannot wholeheartedly surrender your heart to a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.21,0:40:46.11,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,And won't let them heal you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.14,0:40:48.04,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.51,0:40:52.88,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,You cannot love a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.45,0:40:55.45,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Am I not right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.85,0:41:00.36,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, I don't quite understand what you're trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.09,0:41:03.22,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Oh, Natasha-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.19,0:41:07.60,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,My escort has arrived. This is enough talking for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.70,0:41:10.07,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What? What were you talking about just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.83,0:41:12.83,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Did you hear that the host server went down?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.30,0:41:14.20,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,The host server?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.20,0:41:18.91,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Yes, apparently beyond volume 13, all typing has to be done over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.81,0:41:20.91,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.98,0:41:22.11,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,Oh, Iwaya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.41,0:41:25.05,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,The host server just went down and an extra server is in full rotation,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.05,0:41:26.21,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,but the news section gets priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.21,0:41:26.72,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.98,0:41:28.38,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,You may not be able to go home tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.29,0:41:33.99,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.69,0:41:39.06,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I have to do everything over?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.66,0:41:42.10,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.77,0:41:53.64,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,All set!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.26,0:42:08.32,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,She's early.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.19,0:42:10.29,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.53,0:42:14.96,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,You…?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.84,0:42:27.64,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Hey, Fukushima-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.74,0:42:29.74,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I'm sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.41,0:42:35.38,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I know it's rude, but I never would have thought that he would be waiting at my place like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.38,0:42:37.05,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I didn't know what to do after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.75,0:42:40.32,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Anyway, I came running here as fast as I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.02,0:42:42.50,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.10,0:42:54.57,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Well, after a little while, I'll walk you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.24,0:42:57.21,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,He'll probably be gone by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.27,0:42:58.21,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.21,0:42:58.81,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.54,0:43:01.68,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I don't want to be in that house by myself. I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.80,0:43:05.48,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,May I stay here tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.85,0:43:07.85,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,That, I can't…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.12,0:43:08.92,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.88,0:43:14.19,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I'll get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.41,0:43:33.68,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I'm coming, I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.55,0:43:42.22,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Hello, Sumire-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.52,0:43:43.50,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.65,0:43:46.32,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I might not be able to come home tonight, so don't stay up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.32,0:43:47.89,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,What?! Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.16,0:43:49.92,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I can't help it, I have work.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.73,0:43:54.39,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,But I'm lonely! Hey, I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.43,0:43:57.27,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,There's 1000 yen in the usual spot, so go buy something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.27,0:43:58.20,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm going to hang up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.67,0:44:04.71,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Man…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.01,0:44:07.61,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,This pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.85,0:44:21.66,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Shoot, I'm getting even lonelier.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.23,0:44:28.86,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Senpai won't answer the phone…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.00,0:44:30.50,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I wonder if he fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.77,0:44:33.80,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hasumi-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.84,0:44:35.87,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.18,0:44:44.41,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Iwaya's phone is busy…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.22,0:44:50.35,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.12,0:44:56.09,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Was she on the 4th floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.10,0:45:09.73,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.77,0:45:12.27,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I must have had the wrong number.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.51,0:45:15.28,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Plus I just hung up on her, I was so rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.98,0:45:21.88,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,That can't be…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.16,0:45:30.23,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.29,0:45:32.39,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Iwaya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.60,0:45:40.04,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,This is Fukushima~
